Invocation Name: go mahi dot com weekly business hacks
des: These are the weekly life hacks given from business professionals from around the country. During the Master The Start Podcast, we interview professional athletes, billionaires, executives, Forbes #1s and many more. With these guests, we dig into what weekly life hacks all of us "normal" people can apply to our lives to become more successful. This Alexa skill gives you weekly life hacks or actionable tasks that you can apply to you life right now to start dominating the business world.
